      "role": "user",
      "content": "everything is just so quiet now. i walk into the kitchen and i still expect to hear him making coffee or hearing his keys on the counter... but there's nothing. it's just this heavy, empty silence that follows me everywhere. i don't even know why i'm bothering to get out of bed anymore. what's the point of all this just being alone?",
